nodes.title: Setup and Tips
widgets_values:
On first use:
- select models and VAE
- select a default LoRA in each Load LoRA node
- select an upscale model
- add an image in each of the Load Images nodes (purple node)
- select the batch_size in CR Aspect Ratio SDXL
- set the filename_prefix in Save Image to your preferred sub-folder
- save a copy to use as a template

Tips:
- Notes can be opened by clicking on the dots (green nodes)
- Each optional component can be bypassed using logic switches (red nodes)
- The default setting for all logic switches is OFF (1)
- Use Comfyroll Manager to find any missing custom nodes
- Right-click on nodes and select Pin to pin/unpin the node

nodes.title: Workbook Details
widgets_values:
Comfyroll SDXL Workflow Templates
https://civitai.com/models/118005/comfyroll-sdxl-workflow-templates

This template can be used with any SDXL model.
It is not recommended to use SD 1.5 models with this template.

Requires:
WAS Custom Nodes
https://civitai.com/models/20793/was-node-suite-comfyui
Comfyroll Custom Nodes
https://civitai.com/models/87609/comfyroll-custom-nodes-for-comfyui
Searge SDXL Nodes
https://civitai.com/models/111463
SDXL Prompt Styler
https://github.com/twri/sdxl_prompt_styler

August 2023
Akatsuzi
